item.title: love and trust
item.description: a Deep House Mix 1.Flowriders-Russelogy-Bittersuite mix 2.Abicah Soul-Tha Message 3.Dj Spinna and Ovasoul 7-You should be lovin me 4.Walter Stallworth-First Hour 5.Ian friday feat Erro-Found Myself-Osunlade mix 6.Abicah Soul- Versatility 7.Blacklight-1 Luv 8.Reelsoul-Hold on 9.Peven Everett-Feelin Who U are-( Neter- S Blu fix mix) this is my first new mix of the year ,these r some of my favorite traks of 2008. if u like what u hear drop me a line or two. Happy New year to all. p.s there r more mixes @deephousemix.com and deephousesounds.co.uk.peace out greg.
